I think we got bit by the similarity of the glyphs for capital-i, and lowercase-L. "FeatureValueToId" gets a few more hits, while "FeatureValueTold" isn't on the site.

However, even FeatureValueToId doesn't have much visible code or documentation. @zheng-xq, are the docs out of date (so we should remove the old reference and replace it with something more recent)?
